Weingarten Realty Investors said it is negotiating with Portland Fixture L.P., Portland, Ore., on the purchase of 18 shopping centers in the Portland area. 

Weingarten, a real estate investment trust, estimated the value of the property at about $100 million.
Weingarten officials said they have not yet reached an agreement with Portland Fixture, a closely held shopping center developer based in Portland. 

